{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw him a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we drifted again, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wasn't ready, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't ready.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was looking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was older, so I think he was looking at different things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was perhaps looking if he can stay in Poland for while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His sister had survived, you know, so it was sort of different, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, I said to him, that I-- that I will-- I intend to go to Stuttgart, because I heard of the DP.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There could be a lot of Jewish people there, like in Muenchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Ulm or now-- or Muenchen or Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I decided to Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, OK, I will come along as well, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he left it behind him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- and we traveled there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- as a matter of fact, in Stuttgart, he found somebody that survived, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He found on top of-- of a-- a-- a-- his sister-- he was-- during the war, he was, at the age of 19 or something like that, he was briefly married for a few months.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his wife has perished, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but her father has survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somehow, you know, at that stage, he knew that she is not alive, but he still wanted sort of a connection with-- you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this is how his former father-in-law sort of, straightaway, sort of took to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe-- I don't know what had happened-- but I think he the one, really, that sort of got us really together, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, otherwise, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would have-- Ruth, when did you find out about your own family and what happened to them?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't really know exactly what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
